ycliffe's Bible and was completed around 1382.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":1},{"id":1705197,"age":89,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"William Lynne I was born about 1366, in Northamptonshire, England as the son of Lynn. He had at least 1 son with Landresse Candrey."},"et":{"about 1366–":"umbes 1366–Surnud","1366–Male":"1366–Surnud","1371–Female":"1371–Surnud","1384–1421":"1384–1421","1340–Male":"1340–Surnud","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1366":"1366","1384":"1384","1340":"1340","about 1366":"umbes 1366","1382":"1382","1371":"1371","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England"},"fi":{"about 1366–":"noin 1366–Kuollut","1366–Male":"1366–Kuollut","1371–Female":"1371–Kuollut","1384–1421":"1384–1421","1340–Male":"1340–Kuollut","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1366":"1366","1384":"1384","1340":"1340","about 1366":"noin 1366","1382":"1382","1371":"1371","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England"},"fr":{"about 1366–":"environ 1366–Décédé","1366–Male":"1366–Décédé","1371–Female":"1371–Décédée","1384–1421":"1384–1421","1340–Male":"1340–Décédé","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1366":"1366","1384":"1384","1340":"1340","about 1366":"environ 1366","1382":"1382","1371":"1371","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"William Lynne I est né environ 1366, à Northamptonshire, Angleterre, fils de Lynn. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Landresse Candrey."},"de":{"about 1366–":